{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_09_01",
  "title": "kana",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "kanaはさぁ\n見ての通り、立派な大人な訳よ",
      "startTime": 2.3748979251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "え……えぇ、そうですね",
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "なのに最近ガキっぽいオファーばっかくるのはなんで？\n昨日の仕事なんて、幼児番組のゲストよ",
      "startTime": 14.7286394913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "アレか、こころのイメージに引きずられてんのか\nkanaとあいつを一緒くたにするなっての！！",
      "startTime": 22.7286394913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ま……まぁまぁ、落ち着いて\nつまり、大人っぽい仕事がやりたい訳ですね",
      "startTime": 29.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3657.279125699997,
          "startTime": 32.9239457924
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5257.279125699998,
          "startTime": 34.5239457924
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "一応、事務所にこういうオファーがきてまして……\nスポーツメーカーの、テニスラケットのPRなんですが",
      "startTime": 37.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "PRイベントへの出演と、ポスター撮影と……あと\nテニスの練習風景を撮影して、PVに使いたいそうで",
      "startTime": 46.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "テニス？　お、いいじゃん\n紳士淑女のスポーツなら、大人のkanaにぴったり",
      "startTime": 53.8001816907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……そ、そうですね\nでもkanaさん、テニス、経験はあるんですか？",
      "startTime": 60.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "あのねぇ。わざわざアイドル呼ぶってことは\n初心者でも楽に扱えます、ってアピールしたいのよ",
      "startTime": 68.0621544677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "なら、中途半端な経験なんてかえって邪魔でしょ\nその点、kanaは立派に素人だから安心しな",
      "startTime": 76.1621544677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そこは自慢することでもないような……\n……それと、要項にはまだ続きがありまして",
      "startTime": 84.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今回、うちへのオファーは一人だけだったんですが\n当日は別事務所の子と組んでもらうかもしれない、と",
      "startTime": 92.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――PRイベント当日",
      "startTime": 97.8494353769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 99.1494338272
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 99.1494338272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "さてと。イベントが始まるまでまだ少し時間あるし\n今日の仕事相手の顔でも見てくるかな",
      "startTime": 105.4494353769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 108.8494282561
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "ったく、連絡がきたのが直前で\n事前に打ち合わせする時間もなかったからさぁ",
      "startTime": 112.2161020436,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6027.150030800001,
          "startTime": 118.2432520744
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 119.0764395949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、こちらの不手際で……\n……あれ、お客さんが来たみたいですね？",
      "startTime": 119.0764395949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "んー、向こうから挨拶に来たかな？\nふふん、殊勝な心がけじゃん",
      "startTime": 126.0355079954,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3570.095206500014,
          "startTime": 129.6056032019
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3570.095206500014,
          "startTime": 129.6056032019
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 129.6056032019
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 133.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは～！　今日はよろしくお願いします\n……って、あれ～？",
      "startTime": 133.5056042192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "『やさぐれポメラニアン』のコロ子ちゃん？\n前に、ライブバトルで会って以来だよね？",
      "startTime": 139.6389375525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 142.7055970984
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（そう。今日、kanaさんが一緒に仕事をするのは）\n（以前スリクスがライブバトルで戦って、下した相手だ）",
      "startTime": 146.6000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（アイドル業界は狭いから、以前に戦った相手と）\n（別の仕事で会うことも、めずらしくはないんだが……）",
      "startTime": 153.8898962792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 157.7587715623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "あのライブバトルの後、他のグループの子達がみんな\n「kanaさんはいい人」ってめっちゃ褒めてた？",
      "startTime": 162.0254453497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 165.3587715623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "前は全然話せなかったから、会うのを楽しみにしてた？\nえ～、ありがと～～！　kanaも楽しみだったよ～！",
      "startTime": 170.1254453497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 174.2587715623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、一緒に写真撮ろうよ\nマネージャー、カメラマンお願い出来る～？",
      "startTime": 177.1587786831,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5099.998982700015,
          "startTime": 182.2587776658
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7199.998982700009,
          "startTime": 184.3587776658
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8074.554650200014,
          "startTime": 185.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 180.2921048956
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（良かった、二人ともいい雰囲気だな。これなら）\n（前回の恨みを引きずるなんてことはなさそうだ）",
      "startTime": 184.2423103042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 187.5807446636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。コロ子ちゃん\n今日、取材の人達に話す内容って、考えてある？",
      "startTime": 189.847418451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "今日の仕事は基本、新作ラケットのアピールだけど\nでもkana達にも、話は振られるだろうし",
      "startTime": 198.3140851177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 201.8807446636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "テニス経験とか、どんなところが好きか、とか\n聞かれた時に、ネタが被ったらまずいからさ",
      "startTime": 205.9140851177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_01-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんさすが！　って、そんなことないよ～",
      "startTime": 209.8140678243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 213.8140546001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
